# ::tok China and Kyrgyzstan further agree in the communique that the Shanghai Cooperation Organization 's purposes and principles conform to reality and the development trend and the SCO 's activities are conducive to regional peace and stability .
# ::lem china and kyrgyzstan further agree in the communique that the shanghai cooperation organization 's purpose and principle conform to reality and the development trend and the sco 's activity be conducive to regional peace and stability .
# ::pos NNP CC NNP RB VBP IN DT NN IN DT NNP NNP NNP POS NNS CC NNS VB TO NN CC DT NN NN CC DT NNP POS NNS VBP JJ TO JJ NN CC NN .
# ::ner COUNTRY O COUNTRY O O O O O O O ORGANIZATION ORGANIZATION ORGANIZATION O O O O O O O O O O O O O ORGANIZATION O O O O O O O O O O
# ::save-date Mon Jul 6, 2015 ::file PROXY_XIN_ENG_20040922_0123_14.txt
(a / agree-01
      :ARG0 (a2 / and
            :op1 (c / country :wiki "China" :name (n / name :op1 "China"))
            :op2 (c2 / country :wiki "Kyrgyzstan" :name (n2 / name :op1 "Kyrgyzstan")))
      :ARG1 (a3 / and
            :op1 (c4 / conform-01
                  :ARG1 (a4 / and
                        :op1 (p / purpose
                              :poss (o / organization :wiki "Shanghai_Cooperation_Organisation" :name (n3 / name :op1 "Shanghai" :op2 "Cooperation" :op3 "Organization")))
                        :op2 (p2 / principle
                              :poss o))
                  :ARG2 (r / reality))
            :op2 (c5 / conducive
                  :domain (a5 / and
                        :op1 (t / trend
                              :mod (d / develop-02))
                        :op2 (a6 / activity-06
                              :ARG0 o))
                  :purpose (a7 / and
                        :op1 (p3 / peace
                              :mod (r2 / region))
                        :op2 (s / stability
                              :mod r2))))
      :mod (f / further)
      :medium (c3 / communique))

                  :op2 (c3 / country :wiki "Kyrgyzstan" :name (n2 / name :op1 "Kyrgyzstan")))

(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (h / he)
      :ARG1 (b / benefit-01
            :ARG0 (a / and
                  :op1 (v / visit-01
                        :ARG0 (p / person :wiki "Chavalit_Yongchaiyudh" :name (n / name :op1 "Chavalit")
                              :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG2 (p2 / premier

                        :mod (t2 / this))
                  :op2 (v3 / visit-01
                        :ARG0 (a2 / and
                              :op1 (p3 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (l / lead-02

                        :mod (m / mutual)))
            :ARG1 (p4 / promote-02
                  :ARG0 a
                  :ARG1 (a3 / and

                              :degree (f / further))
                        :op2 (c7 / cooperate-01

                              :ARG1 c6

                                    :mod (a4 / all))
                              :ARG1-of (e / efficient-01))))))

# ::id nw.chtb_0302.5 ::date 2012-11-28T21:45:10 ::annotator SDL-AMR-09 ::preferred

# ::id nw.chtb_0302.6 ::date 2012-11-28T21:46:57 ::annotator SDL-AMR-09 ::preferred

# ::tok He said that in recent years , the development of China 's economy has accelerated , and the government and the people of Thailand feel extremely happy .
# ::lem he say that in recent year , the development of china 's economy have accelerate , and the government and the people of thailand feel extremely happy .
# ::pos PRP VBD IN IN JJ NNS , DT NN IN NNP POS NN VBZ VBN , CC DT NN CC DT NNS IN NNP VBP RB JJ .
# ::ner O O O O DURATION DURATION O O O O COUNTRY O O O O O O O O O O O O COUNTRY O O O O
# ::save-date Thu Jan 21, 2016 ::file nw_chtb_0302_6.txt
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (h / he)
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (a2 / accelerate-01
                  :ARG1 (d / develop-02
                        :ARG1 (e / economy
                              :poss (c4 / country :wiki "China" :name (n / name :op1 "China")))))
            :op2 (f / feel-01
                  :ARG0 (a3 / and
                        :op1 (g / government-organization
                              :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                                    :ARG1 (c6 / country :wiki "Thailand" :name (n2 / name :op1 "Thailand"))))
                        :op2 (p / person
                              :mod c6))
                  :ARG1 (h2 / happy-01
                        :ARG1 a3
                        :degree (e2 / extreme)))
            :time (y / year
                  :mod (r / recent))))

# ::pos NNP NNP , DT JJ NN NN , VBD IN DT NN NN VBD DT NN IN NNP NNP NNP IN DT NNP NNP , MD VB DT NNP NN TO NNP IN NNP JJ TO DT JJ IN DT NN IN NN NNP NNP .
# ::ner PERSON PERSON O O O O TITLE O O O O O O O TIME TIME O TITLE PERSON PERSON O O COUNTRY LOCATION O O O O O O O COUNTRY O DATE DATE O O ORDINAL O O O O TITLE PERSON PERSON O
# ::save-date Fri Jul 17, 2015 ::file nw_chtb_0303_2.txt
(a / announce-01
      :ARG0 (p / person :wiki - :name (n / name :op1 "Guofang" :op2 "Shen")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (g4 / government-organization :wiki "Ministry_of_Foreign_Affairs_of_the_People's_Republic_of_China" :name (n2 / name :op1 "Foreign" :op2 "Ministry"))
                  :ARG2 (s / spokesperson)))
      :ARG1 (v / visit-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / person :wiki "Árpád_Göncz" :name (n3 / name :op1 "Gentzs" :op2 "Aerpade")
                  :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (c3 / country :wiki "Hungary" :name (n4 / name :op1 "Hungary" :op2 "Republic"))
                        :ARG2 (p3 / president)))
            :ARG1 (c4 / country :wiki "China" :name (n5 / name :op1 "China"))
            :mod (s2 / state)
            :time (d / date-interval
                  :op1 (d2 / date-entity :month 9 :day 14)
                  :op2 (d3 / date-entity :month 9 :day 17))
            :ARG2-of (i / invite-01
                  :ARG0 (p4 / person :wiki "Jiang_Zemin" :name (n6 / name :op1 "Zemin" :op2 "Jiang")
                        :ARG0-of (h4 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG2 (p5 / president)))))
      :time (c6 / conference
            :mod (n7 / news)
            :ARG1-of (h2 / hold-04
                  :time (d4 / date-entity :dayperiod (a2 / afternoon) :mod (t / today)))))

# ::pos DT JJ NN MD VB TO NNP IN DT JJ .
# ::ner O NATIONALITY O O O O CITY O O ORDINAL O
# ::save-date Tue Dec 17, 2013 ::file nw_chtb_0318_12.txt
(f / fly-01
      :ARG1 (d2 / delegation
            :mod (c3 / country :wiki "Japan"
                  :name (n / name :op1 "Japan")))
      :destination (c4 / city :wiki "Beijing"
            :name (n2 / name :op1 "Beijing"))
      :time (d3 / date-entity :day 2))

# ::id nw.chtb_0318.13 ::date 2012-12-29T13:18:08 ::annotator SDL-AMR-09 ::preferred
# ::snt After the closing ceremonies of the Sports Meet , they will continue to remain in Beijing for two days , to carry out interaction activities with relevant Chinese parties and visit and tour , and return to Japan on 13th .
# ::tok After the closing ceremonies of the Sports Meet , they will continue to remain in Beijing for two days , to carry-out interaction activities with relevant Chinese parties and visit and tour , and return to Japan on 13th .
# ::lem after the closing ceremony of the sports meet , they will continue to remain in beijing for two day , to carry-out interaction activity with relevant chinese party and visit and tour , and return to japan on 13th .
# ::pos IN DT NN NNS IN DT NNP NNP , PRP MD VB TO VB IN NNP IN CD NNS , TO COMP NN NNS IN JJ JJ NNS CC NN CC NN , CC NN TO NNP IN NNP .
# ::ner O O O O O O O O O O O O O O O CITY O DURATION DURATION O O O O O O O NATIONALITY O O O O O O O O O COUNTRY O ORDINAL O
# ::save-date Mon Jul 6, 2015 ::file nw_chtb_0318_13.txt
(a / and
      :op1 (r / remain-01
            :ARG1 (t2 / they)
            :location (c6 / city :wiki "Beijing"
                  :name (n / name :op1 "Beijing"))
            :duration (t3 / temporal-quantity :quant 2
                  :unit (d3 / day))
            :purpose (a4 / and
                        :op1 (c7 / carry-out-03
                              :ARG0 t2
                              :ARG1 (a2 / activity-06
                                    :ARG0 t2
                                    :ARG1 (i / interact-01
                                          :ARG0 t2
                                          :ARG1 (p / party
                                                :mod (c8 / country :wiki "China"
                                                      :name (n2 / name :op1 "China"))
                                                :ARG1-of (r2 / relevant-01)))))
                        :op1 (v / visit-01
                              :ARG0 t2
                              :ARG1 c6)
                        :op3 (t4 / tour-01
                              :ARG0 t2
                              :ARG1 c6))
            :time (a3 / after
                  :op1 (c11 / ceremony
                        :ARG0-of (c / close-01
                              :ARG1 (g / game :wiki "FESPIC_Games"
                                    :name (n4 / name :op1 "Sports" :op2 "Meet"))))))
      :op2 (r3 / return-01
            :ARG1 t2
            :ARG4 (c9 / country :wiki "Japan"
                  :name (n3 / name :op1 "Japan"))
            :time (d4 / date-entity :day 13)))

# ::id nw.chtb_0319.1 ::date 2012-12-29T13:24:43 ::annotator SDL-AMR-09 ::preferred

# ::save-date Tue Jul 28, 2015 ::file nw_chtb_0319_1.txt

      :ARG1 (c2 / change-01
            :ARG2 (p / person :wiki - :name (n2 / name :op1 "Lahagewasulen")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (o / organization :wiki - :name (n4 / name :op1 "Sports" :op2 "Association"))
                        :ARG2 (c / chairman)))
            :ARG3 (p3 / person :wiki - :name (n5 / name :op1 "Lahagewasu")
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 o
                        :ARG2 c)

                        :ARG1 (p4 / paragraph :mod 3)))

                  :ARG1-of (b / broadcast-01
                        :time (t / today))

                                    :ARG1-of (h3 / handicap-01)

# ::id nw.chtb_0322.2 ::date 2012-12-29T13:32:27 ::annotator SDL-AMR-09 ::preferred

(s / start-01
      :ARG1 (c6 / compete-01 :wiki -
            :ARG0 (c5 / country :wiki "China"
                  :name (n5 / name :op1 "China"))
            :ARG1 c4
            :name (n6 / name :op1 "Le" :op2 "Tian" :op3 "Cup")
            :mod (g2 / game :wiki "Go_(game)"
                  :name (n2 / name :op1 "Go")))
      :location (c3 / city :wiki "Busan"
            :name (n3 / name :op1 "Fushan")
            :mod (l2 / large
                  :degree (m / most)

                        :name (n4 / name :op1 "Korea"))
                  :ord (o / ordinal-entity :value 2)))
      :time (t / today))

# ::id nw.chtb_0322.3 ::date 2012-12-29T13:54:58 ::annotator SDL-AMR-09 ::preferred

# ::ner O O ORDINAL O O O O O NATIONALITY O O O O O NATIONALITY O O O O O NUMBER O NUMBER O

      :ARG0 (t / team
            :mod (c4 / country :wiki "China" :name (n / name :op1 "China")))
      :ARG1 (t2 / team
            :mod (c5 / country :wiki "Korea" :name (n2 / name :op1 "Korea"))
            :ARG1-of (s / strong-02
                  :degree (m / more)

                  :ARG2-of (r2 / relative-05)))
      :time (r / round-05
            :ARG1 (c / compete-01)
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity :value 1))
      :quant (s2 / score-entity :op1 4 :op2 3))

# ::id nw.chtb_0322.11 ::date 2012-12-29T14:29:36 ::annotator SDL-AMR-09 ::preferred
# ::snt When receiving reporters telephone interviews , Runan Wang , leader of the Chinese delegation presented that , overall speaking , the strength of the Korean team was stronger than the Chinese team .
# ::tok When receiving reporters telephone interviews , Runan Wang , leader of the Chinese delegation presented that , overall speaking , the strength of the Korean team was stronger than the Chinese team .
# ::lem when receive reporter telephone interview , runan wang , leader of the chinese delegation present that , overall speaking , the strength of the korean team be stronger than the chinese team .

# ::ner O O O O O O PERSON PERSON O TITLE O O NATIONALITY O O O O O O O O O O O NATIONALITY O O O O O NATIONALITY O O
# ::save-date Wed Feb 10, 2016 ::file nw_chtb_0322_11.txt
(p / present-01
      :ARG0 (p2 / person :wiki - :name (n / name :op1 "Runan" :op2 "Wang")
            :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                  :ARG1 (d / delegation
                        :source (c4 / country :wiki "China" :name (n2 / name :op1 "China")))))
      :ARG1 (s / strong-02
            :ARG1 (s2 / strong-02
                  :ARG1 (t / team
                        :mod (c5 / country :wiki "Korea" :name (n3 / name :op1 "Korea"))))
            :degree (m / more)
            :compared-to (s3 / strong-02
                  :ARG1 (t2 / team
                        :mod c4))
            :condition (s5 / speak-01
                  :manner (o / overall)))
      :time (r2 / receive-01
            :ARG0 p2
            :ARG1 (i / interview-01
                  :ARG0 p3
                  :medium (t4 / telephone))
            :ARG2 (p3 / person
                  :ARG0-of (r3 / report-01))))
